{"tid":314563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(大汁撚入)你地平時點買衫？","createTime":"2017-07-09T10:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T11:49:00.000Z","uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af7420cc946dfdac2d3b3fda77eadeafeb9fc2ac","tid":314563,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T10:32:49.000Z","msg":"好多汗個d人出街帶多件衫換<br />\n但係換無幾耐又開始臭<br />\n<br />\n初頭以為人既問題，但有老友話唔關人事係關件衫物料事<br />\n<br />\n睇下件衫成分<br />\n<br />\n100%純綿 頭幾次都無咩野，之後著多幾次有少少汗都已經覺得臭 所以夏天一定唔可以著純綿既衫<br />\n<br />\n暫時我覺得聚脂纖維物料最少味 出成日汗都唔會覺得有幾大浸味<br />\n<br />\n其他大汗撚平時又點買衫？有咩好推介"},{"pid":"763d7b9525cf93353c22d01e1eaf8ddb59980d22","tid":314563,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T10:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0468cb31330d89027ea00c7a004f6aa4c905775","tid":314563,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T10:44:05.000Z","msg":"睇款"},{"pid":"da82ec2ee715798865fad5d265f4db3650359f53","tid":314563,"uid":118246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T10:53:15.000Z","msg":"點著都死 一樣濕晒 乾左之後勁臭"},{"pid":"142595955a5b03dc77a30839603ca84b9de14579","tid":314563,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"704c97a57ac2d6f8855c28af638e3814b5d809f5","tid":314563,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:34:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5db191bd8057b600a385bf64b1f8e80177092309","tid":314563,"uid":106065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"買運動衫<br />\n出汗快乾<br />\n但著完洗個時加滴露殺菌除味"},{"pid":"fa60445bdb2ccbc682ff5292446becef3c13ef2b","tid":314563,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"唔關事。綿係傳統布料算係透氣。<br />\n你果件咁易出事明顯係g數太重同織法太密。<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係要其他物料嘅衫，一係polyester(Nike dry fit 果種), 一係麻囉。"}]}